<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 16:07:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>利库德集团部长制定紧急条例，监禁“损害民族士气”的公民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-seeks-to-imprison-citizens-who-harm-national-morale/0000018b-33a7-d0b2-afff-33e788c00000</link><description>通讯部长卡希正在推动制定法规，如果他认为平民传播了可能损害国家士气或成为敌人宣传基础的信息，他可以指示警察逮捕平民，将他们从家中带走，或没收他们的财产。</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 15:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-seeks-to-imprison-citizens-who-harm-national-morale/0000018b-33a7-d0b2-afff-33e788c00000</guid></item><item><title>美国-以色列向任何帮助营救人质的巴勒斯坦人提供 25 万美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/american-israeli-offers-250-000-to-any-palestinian-who-helps-rescue-a-hostage/0000018b-33ad-dff1-a5eb-fffde61b0000</link><description>导游罗比·伯曼已联系国际联系人，并出现在国际电视上宣传悬赏，希望能释放被哈马斯扣押的人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 14:48:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/american-israeli-offers-250-000-to-any-palestinian-who-helps-rescue-a-hostage/0000018b-33ad-dff1-a5eb-fffde61b0000</guid></item><item><title>马斯克的 X 和哈马斯的数字攻势：加沙是虚假信息的完美风暴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/musks-x-and-hamas-digital-offensive-gaza-is-a-perfect-storm-of-disinformation/0000018b-3331-d450-a3af-7b3d6a050000</link><description>在哈马斯和反疫苗者的帮助下，未经证实的网络攻击报告和以色列国防军背叛以色列的说法被作为伊朗影响网络的一部分排除在外</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 14:34:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/musks-x-and-hamas-digital-offensive-gaza-is-a-perfect-storm-of-disinformation/0000018b-3331-d450-a3af-7b3d6a050000</guid></item><item><title>“这场灾难证明了民主运动的重要性”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/this-catastrophe-proves-the-democracy-movements-importance/0000018b-334e-d1bc-a58b-7befc67b0000</link><description>当哈马斯上周对以色列发起攻击时，民主危机这一关注以色列、波兰和匈牙利民主威胁的新运动不得不重新考虑在布鲁塞尔举行的启动活动。但在呼吁人们关注暴行和人质之后，参与者并没有回避政治</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 14:20:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/this-catastrophe-proves-the-democracy-movements-importance/0000018b-334e-d1bc-a58b-7befc67b0000</guid></item><item><title>美国国家安全顾问：我们从未“忽视”哈马斯对以色列的威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/u-s-national-security-advisor-we-never-took-eye-off-the-ball-on-hamas-threat-to-israel/0000018b-338d-d450-a3af-7b9d34e40000</link><description>沙利文告诉美国有线电视新闻网，以色列官员通知美国，他们周日打开了通往加沙南部的水管</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 14:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/u-s-national-security-advisor-we-never-took-eye-off-the-ball-on-hamas-threat-to-israel/0000018b-338d-d450-a3af-7b9d34e40000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯在就加沙战争进行中东外交旋风之旅后返回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/blinken-to-return-to-israel-following-whirlwind-middle-east-diplomacy-tour-over-gaza-war/0000018b-3363-d1bc-a58b-7be71f120000</link><description>布林肯将从埃及前往以色列，美国一直在与埃及合作，希望缓解日益恶化的加沙人道主义危机，达成暂时开放拉法过境点并建立人道主义走廊的协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 13:55:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/blinken-to-return-to-israel-following-whirlwind-middle-east-diplomacy-tour-over-gaza-war/0000018b-3363-d1bc-a58b-7be71f120000</guid></item><item><title>萨拉·内塔尼亚胡的分社社长因社交媒体帖子“叛徒”而受到批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/sara-netanyahus-bureau-chief-under-fire-for-traitors-social-media-posts/0000018b-3323-d450-a3af-7b3f0fb60000</link><description>萨拉·内塔尼亚胡 (Sara Netanyahu) 顾问齐皮·纳冯 (Tzipi Navon) 在 Facebook 发帖称政治对手和左翼媒体为“叛徒犹太人”后，遭到以色列公务员委员会的停职呼吁</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 13:50:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/sara-netanyahus-bureau-chief-under-fire-for-traitors-social-media-posts/0000018b-3323-d450-a3af-7b3f0fb60000</guid></item><item><title>六个月前我们采访了他们。上周哈马斯谋杀了他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-interviewed-them-six-months-ago-last-week-hamas-murdered-them/0000018b-3316-dff1-a5eb-ffff81820000</link><description>Bilha 和 Yaakobi Yinon 非常喜欢他们位于以色列南部的奇特小木屋。 “这里距离加沙边境围栏 500 米，安静时这里就是人间天堂。”周六他们被烧死</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 12:29:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-interviewed-them-six-months-ago-last-week-hamas-murdered-them/0000018b-3316-dff1-a5eb-ffff81820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须推翻哈马斯的种族灭绝政权。但不是通过杀害无数巴勒斯坦平民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-topple-genocidal-hamas-but-not-by-killing-countless-palestinian-civilians/0000018b-3297-d450-a3af-7b9f89fb0000</link><description>哈马斯屠杀以色列人，直到最终停止。但在以色列地面入侵加沙以推翻哈马斯的边缘，考虑到人口稠密地区战争的性质，巴勒斯坦平民必须不要付出生命的代价</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 12:18:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-topple-genocidal-hamas-but-not-by-killing-countless-palestinian-civilians/0000018b-3297-d450-a3af-7b9f89fb0000</guid></item><item><title>确认哈马斯最严重的暴行：以色列死者身份识别中心内部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article-magazine/confirming-the-worst-hamas-atrocities-where-israel-identifies-the-dead/0000018b-3313-dff1-a5eb-ffffee6f0000</link><description>在以色列拉比死者辨认中心，哈马斯恐怖分子犯下的极端​​残忍行为的证据即使对于那些已经习惯了死亡的人来说也是难以忍受的——包括证实了总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡对被斩首婴儿的描述</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 12:14:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article-magazine/confirming-the-worst-hamas-atrocities-where-israel-identifies-the-dead/0000018b-3313-dff1-a5eb-ffffee6f0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们必须攻击哈马斯，即使以俘虏的生命为代价。否则，我们也会输掉战争”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-must-attack-hamas-even-at-the-cost-of-the-the-captives-otherwise-we-will-lose/0000018b-32a1-dff1-a5eb-fefda1380000</link><description>采访恐怖主义专家阿里尔·梅拉里（Ariel Merari），他敦促“就好像没有人质一样”在加沙发动战争，但他也表示，“没有理由对[巴勒斯坦平民]进行报复，因为他们没有做过任何事而惩罚他们”</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 10:48:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-must-attack-hamas-even-at-the-cost-of-the-the-captives-otherwise-we-will-lose/0000018b-32a1-dff1-a5eb-fefda1380000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲反犹太主义事件增加，以色列驻柏林大使馆表示：“让人想起第三帝国”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/antisemitism-increases-in-europe-israeli-embassy-in-berlin-reminiscent-of-third-reich/0000018b-32b9-d450-a3af-7bbdfa520000</link><description>哈马斯袭击以色列和加沙战争之后，欧洲犹太人报告反犹太主义破坏行为激增，对安全的担忧</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 10:45:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/antisemitism-increases-in-europe-israeli-embassy-in-berlin-reminiscent-of-third-reich/0000018b-32b9-d450-a3af-7bbdfa520000</guid></item><item><title>五枚反坦克导弹向黎巴嫩边境的以色列军队发射；哈马斯火箭袭击以色列中部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article-live/israeli-army-prepares-for-ground-invasion-in-gaza-kills-hamas-commander-who-led-massacres/0000018b-311e-dff1-a5eb-ffff91120000</link><description>以色列国防军暗杀了在以色列两个社区发动致命袭击的哈马斯指挥官 ■ 据卫生部称，加沙遭受了战争中最致命的一天，死亡人数超过 300 人，死亡人数超过 2,300 人 ■ 一名男子在黎巴嫩反坦克炮火中丧生后，以色列国防军进行报复，在边境建立4公里缓冲区 ■ 以色列国防军宣布自战争爆发以来已有279名士兵丧生，超过126人被绑架</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 10:45:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article-live/israeli-army-prepares-for-ground-invasion-in-gaza-kills-hamas-commander-who-led-massacres/0000018b-311e-dff1-a5eb-ffff91120000</guid></item><item><title>BBC 调查记者涉嫌赞扬哈马斯袭击以色列平民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/bbc-investigating-journalists-alleged-praise-for-hamas-attacks-on-israeli-civilians/0000018b-32ae-da5e-abef-bbef4c310000</link><description>BBC 世界阿拉伯语频道的记者被指控撰写和分享支持哈马斯的社交媒体帖子，并声称没有以色列人是平民</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 10:22:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/bbc-investigating-journalists-alleged-praise-for-hamas-attacks-on-israeli-civilians/0000018b-32ae-da5e-abef-bbef4c310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部的贝都因人社区没有受到火箭弹的保护，请关闭警报器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-communities-in-israels-south-left-unprotected-from-rockets/0000018b-3282-d1bc-a58b-7ba7d4d20000</link><description>“我们想过在警报响起时躲进清真寺，但有多少人可以进入那个小地方？此外，这是一个礼拜场所，而不是防空洞，”一位居民说</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 09:57:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-communities-in-israels-south-left-unprotected-from-rockets/0000018b-3282-d1bc-a58b-7ba7d4d20000</guid></item><item><title>加沙卫生部：加沙地带至少2300人死亡，47个家庭被消灭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-health-ministry-at-least-2-300-killed-in-the-gaza-strip-47-families-wiped-out/0000018b-32a6-d450-a3af-7bbe5bbb0000</link><description>“今天，拉斯维加斯大道上没有一个地方是安全的。拉法的一名居民说：“无处可藏”</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 09:32:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-health-ministry-at-least-2-300-killed-in-the-gaza-strip-47-families-wiped-out/0000018b-32a6-d450-a3af-7bbe5bbb0000</guid></item><item><title>美国大使馆为想要离开以色列的美国人安排船只紧急疏散</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/u-s-embassy-organizes-emergency-ship-for-americans-wanting-to-leave-israel/0000018b-3285-dff1-a5eb-fefd8f920000</link><description>周一早上从海法北部港口出发前往塞浦路斯的是美国公民和直系亲属</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 09:10:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/u-s-embassy-organizes-emergency-ship-for-americans-wanting-to-leave-israel/0000018b-3285-dff1-a5eb-fefd8f920000</guid></item><item><title>定居者试图将以色列拖入约旦河西岸的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/settlers-are-trying-to-drag-israel-into-war-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-2fda-d450-a3af-6fdebe030000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 05:25:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/settlers-are-trying-to-drag-israel-into-war-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-2fda-d450-a3af-6fdebe030000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在西方的支持下采取行动的窗口期很窄</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-narrow-window-of-action-sponsored-by-the-west/0000018b-2fec-d450-a3af-6ffcdf5c0000</link><description>南部的大屠杀让以色列公众陷入哀悼，并对加沙局势漠不关心，加沙局势可能很快恶化为人道主义灾难。但随着巴勒斯坦人的困境恶化，来自西方的非凡支持将会减弱</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 03:34:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-narrow-window-of-action-sponsored-by-the-west/0000018b-2fec-d450-a3af-6ffcdf5c0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-15/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-2fda-d1bc-a58b-6fffea810000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 03:06:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-10-15/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-2fda-d1bc-a58b-6fffea810000</guid></item></channel></rss>